title: 11/09/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 11/09/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps all the action from Week 9 in the NFL and College Football. Which matchup stood out to him most this weekend? We're joined by NBC's Chris Simms, Former NFL Lineman Ross Tucker, and Notre Dame Head Football Coach Brian Kelly. Plus, DP remembers his friend, the late Alex Trebek.
